  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Deyr drought crisis modifier to the PDP-BASES Programme</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">To mitigate the current humanitarian crisis caused by drought, strengthening emergency service delivery and response capacities of the Somali Regional Government, supporting eight of the drought affected intervention woredas for the coming five months through the existing partners and programme, to meet immediate and anticipated needs in the following sectors: 1. Health and Nutrition &#x2013; to increase access to emergency, life-saving health and nutrition services for drought affected families suffering from severe and acute malnutrition and associated health concerns. 2. Education &#x2013; to support children and their teachers affected by drought with education materials to continue their education throughout the drought cycle.</narrative>
  </description>
